value.name: Lockdown with my Crush
value.original_name: Swagger Sharma: Lockdown with my Crush
value.overview: Lockdown with your Crush! Isn't it a dream for every one-sided admirer? I expect yes and after this, Shivam turns into a cliche heartbroken lover who attempts to do everything to move on yet as it's been said 'It's difficult to unlove somebody'. Shivam...
